Package: lazysql
Type: Package
Title: Lazy SQL programming
Version: 0.1.2
Authors@R:
    person("Uwe", "Block", email = "u.block.mz@gmail.com",
           role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description:
    Helper functions to build SQL statements
    for dbGetQuery or dbSendQuery under program control.
    More patterns will be added as required.
